  <part id="libfm">
    <title>Libfm Overview</title>
    <para>
Libfm is a library built on top of glib/gio for developing file managers.
It provides some useful file management utilities and related-widgets
missing in gtk+/glib. It's originally developed for use in PCManFM, but
it's carefully designed to be desktop environment-independent and can be
used to develop other file manager-related tools as well.
    </para>
